[normal]The Landscape of Ombudsmen and Complaint Handlers in the 
[normal]UK
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]2.1
[normal]              
[normal]The landscape of ombudsme
[normal]n and complaint handlers in the 
[normal]UK
[normal] 
[normal]dealing with complaints about public services and consumer grievances 
[normal]is
[normal], in my view, 
[normal]crowded
[normal].  T
[normal]his 
[normal]often 
[normal]can be 
[normal]confusing for the citizen who seeks redress for injus
[normal]tice.  
[normal]In order to refine
[normal] the redress landscape, t
[normal]he devolved government
[normal]s in 
[normal]Scotland
[normal] and 
[normal]Wales
[normal] 
[normal]consulted on the roles and remit of various ombudsmen schemes
[normal] in those countries
[normal]. As a result 
[normal]a single 
[normal]offi
[normal]ce of 
[normal]Public Services 
[normal]Ombudsman
[normal] 
[normal]was created 
[normal]in 
[normal]Scotland
