[normal]Access to Parliament’s 
[normal]Ombudsman
[normal] Service
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]3.1
[normal]              
[normal]To e
[normal]nsure that all cit
[normal]izens have direct access to an o
[normal]mbudsman, having exhausted 
[normal]the internal complaints procedure of bodies
[normal], it is important that
[normal] 
[normal]any barriers to accessibility 
